document.full_text: libyan leader muammar gaddafi has sent a message to president barack obama "following the withdrawal of america from the crusader colonial alliance against libya," libya's official news agency jana said on wednesday.

lines_and_colors: libyan leader muammar gaddafi has sent a message to president barack obama "following the withdrawal of america from the crusader colonial alliance against libya," libya's official news agency jana said on wednesday.
